    Scope and Contents
Office files of the Dean of Academic Programs, Larry Shiner (1975-), including correspondence, memoranda, and reports concerning academic program and operations of the office.  
Subjects include graduate assistantships, faculty recruitment, School of Allied Health Professions, budget preparation, coordinator's meetings, faculty assignments, the Instructional Development Unit, internships, student recruitment, and other areas of  academic program administration.  
  
